<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
    <title>${data.title}</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .body {
        margin: 40px auto;
        width: 600px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px #888888;
        padding: 40px;
      }

      .body h2 {
        line-height: 40px;
        font-weight: normal;
        margin-top:  0;
      }

      .body h2 img {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        vertical-align: bottom;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      .body h4 {
        font-weight: normal;
      }

      .body a.btn {
        height: 40px;
        margin: 8px 0 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 3px;
        background-color: #705949;
        padding: 6px 18px;
        outline: 0;
        user-select: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: right;
        color: #ccc;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="body">
      <h2><img src="https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/29349860?s=200&v=4" />请确认你的邮箱地址</h2>
      <h4>点击下方按钮或复制下面的链接进行邮箱验证, 该链接10分钟内有效：</h4>
      <p><a href="${data.link}" target="_blank">${data.link}</a></p>
      <a class="btn" href="${data.link}" target="_blank">马上验证</a>
      <hr />
      <p class="footer">
        <span>来自TRPG Engine团队</span>
        &nbsp;
        <span>${new Date().Format('yyyy-MM-dd hh:mm')}</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
